Financial Aid System Applicant ID: Whatever ID used to track - numbers only, no decimals, etc.
Recommended Award: Dollar amount from SSS, FAST, etc.
Est Household Contribution: What the family offers to pay in dollars
Total Income: Total income in dollars of all parents
Total Available for Tuition: What SSS, FAST, etc. says they should have available to pay tuition (in $)
Total Net Worth: Total net worth of all parents
P1 Alumni Academy: Did parent one attend the school (0 = false, 1=true)
P1 Alumni Camp: Did parent one attend summer camp(0=false, 1=true)
P2 Alumni Academy: Did parent two attend the school (0 = false, 1=true)
P2 Alumni Camp: Did parent two attend summer camp(0=false, 1=true)
Sum Alum: Summation of number of programs parents attended (e.g., 0, 1, 4, etc.)
Sum Review: Numerical summation of how many reviews (e.g., 1, 2, 3, or 4)
Art Rating: Artistic rating with one decimal (e.g., 1.1, 4.5, etc.)
Attended Sum: Summation of number of summer programs  attended (e.g., 0, 1, 4, etc.)
